import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import {Playground} from 'docz'
import Tabs from './Tabs'
import Tab from './Tab'
import TabList from './TabList'
import TabPanels from './TabPanels'
import ClearFix from './ClearFix'
import Box from './Box'
import Text from './Text'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"tabs"}}>{`Tabs`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Tabs>
  <TabList>
    <Tab>Option 1</Tab>
    <Tab>Option 2</Tab>
  </TabList>
  <ClearFix />
  <TabPanels>
    <Box bg="red">
      <Text>Wowee</Text>
    </Box>
    <Box bg="blue">
      <Text>Not so Wowee</Text>
    </Box>
  </TabPanels>
</Tabs>`} __scope={{props,Tabs,Tab,TabList,TabPanels,ClearFix,Box,Text}}>
  <Tabs>
    <TabList>
      <Tab>Option 1</Tab>
      <Tab>Option 2</Tab>
    </TabList>
    <ClearFix />
    <TabPanels>
      <Box bg="red"><Text>Wowee</Text></Box>
      <Box bg="blue"><Text>Not so Wowee</Text></Box>
    </TabPanels>
  </Tabs>
</Playground></MDXTag>
